{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GmJ3Jjg3cwEWBp2oF2cDPr","type":"tool_result","content":"649\t### FR-14: Player-Facing API Endpoints\n650\t\n651\tAPI for the frontend to display challenges, progress, points, and crate history.\n652\t\n653\tPlayer-facing note: all challenge and reward updates are async from `game.settled`. Progress, points, and crate history should appear within seconds after settlement, but are not guaranteed to be visible in the same request path that triggered settlement.\n654\t\n655\t**Endpoints:**\n656\t\n657\t| Method | Path | Description |\n658\t|---|---|---|\n659\t| `GET` | `/challenges/mine` | Returns active + recently completed challenges for the authenticated user. Triggers lazy assignment if needed. |\n660\t| `GET` | `/challenges/mine/history` | Paginated list of past challenge completions |\n661\t| `GET` | `/points/mine` | Returns current point balance and lifetime earned |\n662\t| `GET` | `/points/mine/history` | Paginated points ledger history from `point_grants` |\n663\t| `GET` | `/crates/mine` | Paginated crate drop history with `status` (`pending`, `granted`, `failed`) |\n664\t| `GET` | `/dogpile/current` | Returns current/next Dogpile event (if any) with countdown to start or end |\n665\t| `GET` | `/dogpile/schedule` | Returns upcoming Dogpile events |\n666\t\n667\t**`GET /challenges/mine` response shape:**\n668\t```typescript\n669\t{\n670\t  daily: {\n671\t    challenges: Array<{\n672\t      id: number;\n673\t      title: string;\n674\t      description: string;\n675\t      progress: number;\n676\t      target: number;\n677\t      status: \"active\" | \"completed\" | \"expired\";\n678\t      reward: { type: \"points\" | \"crate\"; amount?: number };\n679\t      completedAt: string | null;\n680\t    }>;\n681\t    bonus: {\n682\t      title: string;\n683\t      required: number;\n684\t      completed: number;\n685\t      status: \"active\" | \"completed\";\n686\t      reward: { type: \"points\" | \"crate\"; amount?: number };\n687\t    } | null;\n688\t    resetsAt: string;  // ISO 8601\n689\t  };\n690\t  weekly: {\n691\t    /* same shape; `bonus` is `null` in M1 unless a weekly completion bonus is explicitly configured */\n692\t  };\n693\t  onboarding: {\n694\t    steps: Array<{ /* same shape + locked: boolean */ }>;\n695\t    completed: boolean;\n696\t  } | null;  // null after onboarding complete\n697\t}\n698\t```\n699\t\n700\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n701\t- [ ] `GET /challenges/mine` returns daily, weekly, and onboarding sections\n702\t- [ ] Lazy assignment triggered on first call after daily/weekly reset\n703\t- [ ] Response includes progress, target, status, reward, and reset countdown\n704\t- [ ] Onboarding section shows locked steps (prerequisite not yet met) with `locked: true`\n705\t- [ ] Onboarding section is `null` for players who completed all onboarding steps\n706\t- [ ] `GET /points/mine` returns `{ balance, lifetimeEarned }`\n707\t- [ ] `GET /points/mine/history` returns paginated point grant rows with source metadata and timestamps from `point_grants`\n708\t- [ ] `GET /challenges/mine/history` returns paginated past completions\n709\t- [ ] `GET /crates/mine` returns paginated crate drops with type, amount, timestamp, and payout status semantics (`pending` queued, `granted` applied, `failed` needs retry/manual review)\n710\t- [ ] `GET /dogpile/current` returns active event with countdown to `ends_at`, or next scheduled event with countdown to `starts_at`\n711\t- [ ] All endpoints require JWT auth (existing middleware)\n712\t- [ ] All endpoints use standard error format (existing `errorResponse` helper)\n713\t\n714\t---\n715\t\n716\t### FR-15: Admin API Endpoints\n717\t\n718\tInternal endpoints for operators to manage campaigns, challenges, Dogpile events, and reward tuning. Fraud review and richer analytics are deferred until the lightweight M1 loop proves useful.\n719\t\n720\t| Method | Path | Description |\n721\t|---|---|---|\n722\t| `POST` | `/admin/campaigns` | Create a campaign |\n723\t| `PUT` | `/admin/campaigns/:id` | Update campaign (toggle active, change dates) |\n724\t| `POST` | `/admin/challenges` | Create a challenge template in a campaign |\n725\t| `PUT` | `/admin/challenges/:id` | Update challenge (toggle active, change threshold/reward) |\n726\t| `POST` | `/admin/dogpile` | Schedule a Dogpile event |\n727\t| `PUT` | `/admin/dogpile/:id` | Update/cancel a Dogpile event |\n728\t| `GET` | `/admin/dogpile` | List all Dogpile events |\n729\t| `PUT` | `/admin/reward-config/:key` | Update a reward config value |\n730\t| `GET` | `/admin/reward-config` | List all reward config values |\n731\t| `GET` | `/admin/reward-pool` | Reward pool balance and lifetime stats |\n732\t\n733\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n734\t- [ ] All admin endpoints require operator-level auth\n735\t- [ ] Campaign CRUD: create, update, toggle active. Cannot delete (soft-disable only).\n736\t- [ ] Challenge CRUD: create, update, toggle active within a campaign\n737\t- [ ] Dogpile scheduling: create events, cancel future events, cannot modify active events\n738\t- [ ] Reward config: read all, update by key\n739\t- [ ] Reward pool: read current balance, lifetime funded, lifetime paid\n740\t\n741\t---\n742\t\n743\t## Success Criteria\n744\t\n745\t1. A player who plays 5 coinflip games in a day sees their \"Play 5 games\" daily challenge progress from 0/5 to 5/5 and transition to completed — without any manual action.\n746\t2. A player who completes all 3 daily challenges receives a bonus crate.\n747\t3. A new player who has never played sees onboarding challenges guiding them through their first games.\n748\t4. Points accumulate proportionally to wagered volume across all games."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2e700c10-4389-4a9a-beb2-50db732591da","uuid":"af87e17a-ac2d-4d68-9ef7-6f685ad07d47","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:52:15.035Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/400-challenge-engine/spec.md","content":"### FR-14: Player-Facing API Endpoints\n\nAPI for the frontend to display challenges, progress, points, and crate history.\n\nPlayer-facing note: all challenge and reward updates are async from `game.settled`. Progress, points, and crate history should appear within seconds after settlement, but are not guaranteed to be visible in the same request path that triggered settlement.\n\n**Endpoints:**\n\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `GET` | `/challenges/mine` | Returns active + recently completed challenges for the authenticated user. Triggers lazy assignment if needed. |\n| `GET` | `/challenges/mine/history` | Paginated list of past challenge completions |\n| `GET` | `/points/mine` | Returns current point balance and lifetime earned |\n| `GET` | `/points/mine/history` | Paginated points ledger history from `point_grants` |\n| `GET` | `/crates/mine` | Paginated crate drop history with `status` (`pending`, `granted`, `failed`) |\n| `GET` | `/dogpile/current` | Returns current/next Dogpile event (if any) with countdown to start or end |\n| `GET` | `/dogpile/schedule` | Returns upcoming Dogpile events |\n\n**`GET /challenges/mine` response shape:**\n```typescript\n{\n  daily: {\n    challenges: Array<{\n      id: number;\n      title: string;\n      description: string;\n      progress: number;\n      target: number;\n      status: \"active\" | \"completed\" | \"expired\";\n      reward: { type: \"points\" | \"crate\"; amount?: number };\n      completedAt: string | null;\n    }>;\n    bonus: {\n      title: string;\n      required: number;\n      completed: number;\n      status: \"active\" | \"completed\";\n      reward: { type: \"points\" | \"crate\"; amount?: number };\n    } | null;\n    resetsAt: string;  // ISO 8601\n  };\n  weekly: {\n    /* same shape; `bonus` is `null` in M1 unless a weekly completion bonus is explicitly configured */\n  };\n  onboarding: {\n    steps: Array<{ /* same shape + locked: boolean */ }>;\n    completed: boolean;\n  } | null;  // null after onboarding complete\n}\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] `GET /challenges/mine` returns daily, weekly, and onboarding sections\n- [ ] Lazy assignment triggered on first call after daily/weekly reset\n- [ ] Response includes progress, target, status, reward, and reset countdown\n- [ ] Onboarding section shows locked steps (prerequisite not yet met) with `locked: true`\n- [ ] Onboarding section is `null` for players who completed all onboarding steps\n- [ ] `GET /points/mine` returns `{ balance, lifetimeEarned }`\n- [ ] `GET /points/mine/history` returns paginated point grant rows with source metadata and timestamps from `point_grants`\n- [ ] `GET /challenges/mine/history` returns paginated past completions\n- [ ] `GET /crates/mine` returns paginated crate drops with type, amount, timestamp, and payout status semantics (`pending` queued, `granted` applied, `failed` needs retry/manual review)\n- [ ] `GET /dogpile/current` returns active event with countdown to `ends_at`, or next scheduled event with countdown to `starts_at`\n- [ ] All endpoints require JWT auth (existing middleware)\n- [ ] All endpoints use standard error format (existing `errorResponse` helper)\n\n---\n\n### FR-15: Admin API Endpoints\n\nInternal endpoints for operators to manage campaigns, challenges, Dogpile events, and reward tuning. Fraud review and richer analytics are deferred until the lightweight M1 loop proves useful.\n\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| `POST` | `/admin/campaigns` | Create a campaign |\n| `PUT` | `/admin/campaigns/:id` | Update campaign (toggle active, change dates) |\n| `POST` | `/admin/challenges` | Create a challenge template in a campaign |\n| `PUT` | `/admin/challenges/:id` | Update challenge (toggle active, change threshold/reward) |\n| `POST` | `/admin/dogpile` | Schedule a Dogpile event |\n| `PUT` | `/admin/dogpile/:id` | Update/cancel a Dogpile event |\n| `GET` | `/admin/dogpile` | List all Dogpile events |\n| `PUT` | `/admin/reward-config/:key` | Update a reward config value |\n| `GET` | `/admin/reward-config` | List all reward config values |\n| `GET` | `/admin/reward-pool` | Reward pool balance and lifetime stats |\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] All admin endpoints require operator-level auth\n- [ ] Campaign CRUD: create, update, toggle active. Cannot delete (soft-disable only).\n- [ ] Challenge CRUD: create, update, toggle active within a campaign\n- [ ] Dogpile scheduling: create events, cancel future events, cannot modify active events\n- [ ] Reward config: read all, update by key\n- [ ] Reward pool: read current balance, lifetime funded, lifetime paid\n\n---\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n1. A player who plays 5 coinflip games in a day sees their \"Play 5 games\" daily challenge progress from 0/5 to 5/5 and transition to completed — without any manual action.\n2. A player who completes all 3 daily challenges receives a bonus crate.\n3. A new player who has never played sees onboarding challenges guiding them through their first games.\n4. Points accumulate proportionally to wagered volume across all games.","numLines":100,"startLine":649,"totalLines":926}}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KhJ3hwWBUymuJMxAovoQj6","type":"tool_result","content":"1\timport { Hono } from \"hono\";\n2\timport { cors } from \"hono/cors\";\n3\timport { serve } from \"@hono/node-server\";\n4\timport { Connection, PublicKey } from \"@solana/web3.js\";\n5\timport postgres from \"postgres\";\n6\timport { loadConfig } from \"./config.js\";\n7\timport { createDb } from \"./db.js\";\n8\timport { createAuthDb } from \"./auth-db.js\";\n9\timport { createCoinflipRoutes } from \"./routes/create.js\";\n10\timport { createLordRoutes } from \"./routes/lord-create.js\";\n11\timport { createRoundsRoutes } from \"./routes/rounds.js\";\n12\timport { createCloseCallRoutes } from \"./routes/closecall.js\";\n13\timport { createHealthRoutes } from \"./routes/health.js\";\n14\timport { createProfileRoutes } from \"./routes/profile.js\";\n15\timport { createPublicProfileRoutes } from \"./routes/public-profile.js\";\n16\timport { createPriceRoutes } from \"./routes/price.js\";\n17\timport { createAuthRoutes } from \"./routes/auth.js\";\n18\timport { createReferralRoutes } from \"./routes/referral.js\";\n19\timport { createLeaderboardRoutes } from \"./routes/leaderboard.js\";\n20\timport { createChallengeRoutes } from \"./routes/challenges.js\";\n21\timport { createInternalRoutes } from \"./routes/internal.js\";\n22\timport { swaggerUI } from \"@hono/swagger-ui\";\n23\timport { spec } from \"./openapi.js\";\n24\timport { createJwtAuthMiddleware } from \"./middleware/jwt-auth.js\";\n25\timport { createRateLimitMiddleware } from \"./middleware/rate-limit.js\";\n26\timport { createSettlementWorker } from \"./worker/settlement.js\";\n27\timport { settleRound } from \"./worker/settle-tx.js\";\n28\timport { createRetrySettler } from \"./worker/retry.js\";\n29\timport { createPdaWatcher } from \"./worker/pda-watcher.js\";\n30\timport { createCloseCallClockWorker } from \"./worker/closecall-clock.js\";\n31\timport { createEventWorker, registerHandler, EventTypes } from \"./queue/index.js\";\n32\timport { createClaimHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/referral-claim.js\";\n33\timport { createRewardPoolFundHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/reward-pool-fund.js\";\n34\timport { createPointsGrantHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/points-grant.js\";\n35\timport { createCrateDropHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/crate-drop.js\";\n36\timport { createGameSettledHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/game-settled.js\";\n37\timport { fetchSolPrice } from \"./routes/price.js\";\n38\timport { logger } from \"./logger.js\";\n39\t\n40\tconst config = loadConfig();\n41\t\n42\t// Single postgres pool shared by game DB, auth DB, and all workers\n43\tconst sql = postgres(config.databaseUrl);\n44\tconst db = createDb(config.databaseUrl, sql);\n45\tconst authDb = createAuthDb(sql);\n46\t\n47\tconst connection = new Connection(config.rpcUrl, {\n48\t  commitment: \"confirmed\",\n49\t  ...(config.wsRpcUrl ? { wsEndpoint: config.wsRpcUrl } : {}),\n50\t});\n51\t\n52\tconst app = new Hono();\n53\t\n54\tapp.use(\n55\t  \"*\",\n56\t  cors({\n57\t    origin: \"*\", // Safe: auth is bearer-token only (no cookies). Restrict if cookie auth is ever added.\n58\t    allowMethods: [\"GET\", \"POST\", \"OPTIONS\"],\n59\t    allowHeaders: [\"Content-Type\", \"Authorization\", \"X-Admin-Token\"],\n60\t  }),\n61\t);\n62\t\n63\t// Request logging — correlate frontend fetch timing with server-side processing\n64\tapp.use(\"*\", async (c, next) => {\n65\t  const start = Date.now();\n66\t  await next();\n67\t  const ms = Date.now() - start;\n68\t  const method = c.req.method;\n69\t  const path = c.req.path;\n70\t  // Skip noisy health checks and OPTIONS preflight\n71\t  if (path === \"/health\" || method === \"OPTIONS\") return;\n72\t  logger.debug(\"request\", { method, path, status: c.res.status, ms });\n73\t});\n74\t\n75\t// API docs — Swagger UI + raw OpenAPI spec\n76\tapp.get(\"/docs\", swaggerUI({ url: \"/openapi.json\" }));\n77\tapp.get(\"/openapi.json\", (c) => c.json(spec));\n78\t\n79\t// Auth routes — no JWT middleware (these are the login endpoints)\n80\t// Lighter rate limiting by IP for auth endpoints\n81\tapp.use(\n82\t  \"/auth/*\",\n83\t  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n84\t    perWallet: 20,\n85\t    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n86\t    windowMs: 60_000,\n87\t  }),\n88\t);\n89\t\n90\tapp.route(\n91\t  \"/auth\",\n92\t  createAuthRoutes({\n93\t    authDb,\n94\t    db,\n95\t    jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret,\n96\t    cluster: config.cluster,\n97\t    challengeTtlSeconds: config.challengeTtlSeconds,\n98\t    accessTokenTtlSeconds: config.accessTokenTtlSeconds,\n99\t    refreshTokenTtlDays: config.refreshTokenTtlDays,\n100\t  }),\n101\t);\n102\t\n103\t// Profile routes — authenticated GET endpoints (require JWT on all methods)\n104\tapp.use(\n105\t  \"/profile/*\",\n106\t  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }),\n107\t);\n108\tapp.route(\"/profile\", createProfileRoutes({ db }));\n109\t\n110\t// Public profile routes — no auth required\n111\tapp.route(\"/public-profile\", createPublicProfileRoutes({ db }));\n112\t\n113\t// Referral routes — authenticated GET + POST endpoints (require JWT on all methods)\n114\tapp.use(\n115\t  \"/referral/*\",\n116\t  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }),\n117\t);\n118\tapp.route(\"/referral\", createReferralRoutes({ db, sql, config }));\n119\t\n120\t// JWT auth middleware for game endpoints\n121\tapp.use(\n122\t  \"/coinflip/*\",\n123\t  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret }),\n124\t);\n125\tapp.use(\n126\t  \"/lord/*\",\n127\t  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret }),\n128\t);\n129\t\n130\t// Rate limiting — per-wallet and global limits on POST requests\n131\tapp.use(\n132\t  \"/coinflip/*\",\n133\t  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n134\t    perWallet: config.rateLimitPerWallet,\n135\t    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n136\t    windowMs: 60_000,\n137\t  }),\n138\t);\n139\tapp.use(\n140\t  \"/lord/*\",\n141\t  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n142\t    perWallet: config.rateLimitPerWallet,\n143\t    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n144\t    windowMs: 60_000,\n145\t  }),\n146\t);\n147\t\n148\t// Settlement infrastructure — must be created before routes (routes use pdaWatcher)\n149\tconst entropyAccount = new PublicKey(config.entropyAccount);\n150\tconst retrySettler = createRetrySettler({\n151\t  db,\n152\t  connection,\n153\t  settleRound: (pda) =>\n154\t    settleRound(\n155\t      { db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair, entropyAccount, referralDefaultRateBps: config.referralDefaultRateBps },\n156\t      pda,\n157\t    ),\n158\t});\n159\t\n160\t// PDA watcher — WebSocket-based instant join detection\n161\tconst pdaWatcher = createPdaWatcher({\n162\t  connection,\n163\t  serverKey: config.serverKeypair.publicKey,\n164\t  db,\n165\t  onJoinDetected: async (pda, targetSlot) => {\n166\t    // Update DB phase if still in 'created'\n167\t    const round = await db.getRoundByPda(pda);\n168\t    if (round && round.phase === \"created\") {\n169\t      await db.updateRoundPhase(pda, \"locked\", {\n170\t        target_slot: targetSlot.toString(),\n171\t      });\n172\t      await db.insertOperatorEvent(pda, \"match_detected\", {\n173\t        targetSlot: targetSlot.toString(),\n174\t        source: \"pda-watcher\",\n175\t        game: round.game,\n176\t      });\n177\t    }\n178\t\n179\t    // Check if target slot already passed — settle immediately if so\n180\t    const currentSlot = await connection.getSlot();\n181\t    if (BigInt(currentSlot) >= targetSlot) {\n182\t      await retrySettler.attemptSettle(pda);\n183\t      pdaWatcher.unwatch(pda);\n184\t    }\n185\t    // If target slot not reached yet, poll worker will pick it up next cycle\n186\t  },\n187\t});\n188\t\n189\tconst worker = createSettlementWorker({\n190\t  db,\n191\t  connection,\n192\t  serverKey: config.serverKeypair.publicKey,\n193\t  pollIntervalMs: config.workerPollIntervalMs,\n194\t  onSettleReady: async (pda) => {\n195\t    await retrySettler.attemptSettle(pda);\n196\t    pdaWatcher.unwatch(pda); // clean up subscription after settlement\n197\t  },\n198\t  isFinalized: (pda) => retrySettler.isFinalized(pda),\n199\t});\n200\tworker.start();\n201\t\n202\t// Close Call clock worker — fetches boundary prices + settles open rounds\n203\t// Rounds are created on-demand by players via /closecall/bet\n204\tconst closeCallClock = createCloseCallClockWorker({\n205\t  connection,\n206\t  serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair,\n207\t  db,\n208\t});\n209\tcloseCallClock.start();\n210\t\n211\t// Register event handlers before starting the worker\n212\tregisterHandler(\n213\t  EventTypes.REFERRAL_CLAIM_REQUESTED,\n214\t  createClaimHandler({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair }),\n215\t);\n216\tregisterHandler(\n217\t  EventTypes.GAME_SETTLED,\n218\t  createGameSettledHandler({ db }),\n219\t);\n220\tregisterHandler(\n221\t  EventTypes.REWARD_POOL_FUND,\n222\t  createRewardPoolFundHandler({ db }),\n223\t);\n224\tregisterHandler(\n225\t  EventTypes.POINTS_GRANT,\n226\t  createPointsGrantHandler({\n227\t    db,\n228\t    getSolPrice: async () => {\n229\t      const result = await fetchSolPrice();\n230\t      return result?.price ?? null;\n231\t    },\n232\t  }),\n233\t);\n234\tregisterHandler(\n235\t  EventTypes.CRATE_DROP,\n236\t  createCrateDropHandler({ db }),\n237\t);\n238\t\n239\t// Event queue worker — processes async side-effects (rewards, notifications, etc.)\n240\tconst eventWorker = createEventWorker(sql, {\n241\t  pollIntervalMs: config.eventQueuePollMs,\n242\t});\n243\teventWorker.start();\n244\tlogger.info(\"Event queue worker started\", {\n245\t  pollIntervalMs: config.eventQueuePollMs,\n246\t});\n247\t\n248\t// Game-specific routes\n249\tapp.route(\n250\t  \"/coinflip\",\n251\t  createCoinflipRoutes({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair, pdaWatcher }),\n252\t);\n253\tapp.route(\n254\t  \"/lord\",\n255\t  createLordRoutes({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair, pdaWatcher }),\n256\t);\n257\t\n258\t// Close Call — JWT + rate limiting on POST /bet (co-signs with server keypair)\n259\tapp.use(\n260\t  \"/closecall/bet\",\n261\t  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret }),\n262\t);\n263\tapp.use(\n264\t  \"/closecall/bet\",\n265\t  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n266\t    perWallet: config.rateLimitPerWallet,\n267\t    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n268\t    windowMs: 60_000,\n269\t  }),\n270\t);\n271\t\n272\t// Close Call routes (read endpoints are public, /bet is auth'd above)\n273\tapp.route(\"/closecall\", createCloseCallRoutes({\n274\t  db,\n275\t  connection,\n276\t  serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair,\n277\t  clockWorker: closeCallClock,\n278\t}));\n279\t\n280\t// Challenge routes — authenticated GET endpoints (require JWT on all methods)\n281\tapp.use(\n282\t  \"/challenges/*\",\n283\t  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }),\n284\t);\n285\tapp.route(\"/challenges\", createChallengeRoutes({ db }));\n286\t\n287\t// Leaderboard routes — public, no auth\n288\tapp.route(\"/leaderboard\", createLeaderboardRoutes({ db }));\n289\t\n290\t// Price routes — public, no auth\n291\tapp.route(\"/price\", createPriceRoutes());\n292\t\n293\t// Round verification routes\n294\tapp.route(\"/rounds\", createRoundsRoutes({ db }));\n295\t\n296\t// Health endpoint — wired after worker exists so we can query its status\n297\tapp.route(\n298\t  \"/health\",\n299\t  createHealthRoutes({\n300\t    db,\n301\t    sql,\n302\t    isWorkerRunning: () => worker.isRunning,\n303\t  }),\n304\t);\n305\t\n306\t// Internal admin routes — only registered when ADMIN_TOKEN is set (dev/devnet only)\n307\tif (config.adminToken) {\n308\t  app.route(\"/internal\", createInternalRoutes({ config, sql }));\n309\t  logger.warn(\"Admin routes enabled at /internal — do NOT set ADMIN_TOKEN in production\");\n310\t}\n311\t\n312\tconst port = config.port;\n313\tlogger.info(\"fairness-backend started\", { port });\n314\t\n315\tserve({\n316\t  fetch: app.fetch,\n317\t  port,\n318\t  hostname: \"0.0.0.0\",\n319\t});\n320\t\n321\texport default {\n322\t  port,\n323\t  fetch: app.fetch,\n324\t};\n325\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2e700c10-4389-4a9a-beb2-50db732591da","uuid":"5dd45521-dd3a-4e95-813a-3936935408d2","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:52:15.416Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/index.ts","content":"import { Hono } from \"hono\";\nimport { cors } from \"hono/cors\";\nimport { serve } from \"@hono/node-server\";\nimport { Connection, PublicKey } from \"@solana/web3.js\";\nimport postgres from \"postgres\";\nimport { loadConfig } from \"./config.js\";\nimport { createDb } from \"./db.js\";\nimport { createAuthDb } from \"./auth-db.js\";\nimport { createCoinflipRoutes } from \"./routes/create.js\";\nimport { createLordRoutes } from \"./routes/lord-create.js\";\nimport { createRoundsRoutes } from \"./routes/rounds.js\";\nimport { createCloseCallRoutes } from \"./routes/closecall.js\";\nimport { createHealthRoutes } from \"./routes/health.js\";\nimport { createProfileRoutes } from \"./routes/profile.js\";\nimport { createPublicProfileRoutes } from \"./routes/public-profile.js\";\nimport { createPriceRoutes } from \"./routes/price.js\";\nimport { createAuthRoutes } from \"./routes/auth.js\";\nimport { createReferralRoutes } from \"./routes/referral.js\";\nimport { createLeaderboardRoutes } from \"./routes/leaderboard.js\";\nimport { createChallengeRoutes } from \"./routes/challenges.js\";\nimport { createInternalRoutes } from \"./routes/internal.js\";\nimport { swaggerUI } from \"@hono/swagger-ui\";\nimport { spec } from \"./openapi.js\";\nimport { createJwtAuthMiddleware } from \"./middleware/jwt-auth.js\";\nimport { createRateLimitMiddleware } from \"./middleware/rate-limit.js\";\nimport { createSettlementWorker } from \"./worker/settlement.js\";\nimport { settleRound } from \"./worker/settle-tx.js\";\nimport { createRetrySettler } from \"./worker/retry.js\";\nimport { createPdaWatcher } from \"./worker/pda-watcher.js\";\nimport { createCloseCallClockWorker } from \"./worker/closecall-clock.js\";\nimport { createEventWorker, registerHandler, EventTypes } from \"./queue/index.js\";\nimport { createClaimHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/referral-claim.js\";\nimport { createRewardPoolFundHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/reward-pool-fund.js\";\nimport { createPointsGrantHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/points-grant.js\";\nimport { createCrateDropHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/crate-drop.js\";\nimport { createGameSettledHandler } from \"./queue/handlers/game-settled.js\";\nimport { fetchSolPrice } from \"./routes/price.js\";\nimport { logger } from \"./logger.js\";\n\nconst config = loadConfig();\n\n// Single postgres pool shared by game DB, auth DB, and all workers\nconst sql = postgres(config.databaseUrl);\nconst db = createDb(config.databaseUrl, sql);\nconst authDb = createAuthDb(sql);\n\nconst connection = new Connection(config.rpcUrl, {\n  commitment: \"confirmed\",\n  ...(config.wsRpcUrl ? { wsEndpoint: config.wsRpcUrl } : {}),\n});\n\nconst app = new Hono();\n\napp.use(\n  \"*\",\n  cors({\n    origin: \"*\", // Safe: auth is bearer-token only (no cookies). Restrict if cookie auth is ever added.\n    allowMethods: [\"GET\", \"POST\", \"OPTIONS\"],\n    allowHeaders: [\"Content-Type\", \"Authorization\", \"X-Admin-Token\"],\n  }),\n);\n\n// Request logging — correlate frontend fetch timing with server-side processing\napp.use(\"*\", async (c, next) => {\n  const start = Date.now();\n  await next();\n  const ms = Date.now() - start;\n  const method = c.req.method;\n  const path = c.req.path;\n  // Skip noisy health checks and OPTIONS preflight\n  if (path === \"/health\" || method === \"OPTIONS\") return;\n  logger.debug(\"request\", { method, path, status: c.res.status, ms });\n});\n\n// API docs — Swagger UI + raw OpenAPI spec\napp.get(\"/docs\", swaggerUI({ url: \"/openapi.json\" }));\napp.get(\"/openapi.json\", (c) => c.json(spec));\n\n// Auth routes — no JWT middleware (these are the login endpoints)\n// Lighter rate limiting by IP for auth endpoints\napp.use(\n  \"/auth/*\",\n  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n    perWallet: 20,\n    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n    windowMs: 60_000,\n  }),\n);\n\napp.route(\n  \"/auth\",\n  createAuthRoutes({\n    authDb,\n    db,\n    jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret,\n    cluster: config.cluster,\n    challengeTtlSeconds: config.challengeTtlSeconds,\n    accessTokenTtlSeconds: config.accessTokenTtlSeconds,\n    refreshTokenTtlDays: config.refreshTokenTtlDays,\n  }),\n);\n\n// Profile routes — authenticated GET endpoints (require JWT on all methods)\napp.use(\n  \"/profile/*\",\n  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }),\n);\napp.route(\"/profile\", createProfileRoutes({ db }));\n\n// Public profile routes — no auth required\napp.route(\"/public-profile\", createPublicProfileRoutes({ db }));\n\n// Referral routes — authenticated GET + POST endpoints (require JWT on all methods)\napp.use(\n  \"/referral/*\",\n  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }),\n);\napp.route(\"/referral\", createReferralRoutes({ db, sql, config }));\n\n// JWT auth middleware for game endpoints\napp.use(\n  \"/coinflip/*\",\n  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret }),\n);\napp.use(\n  \"/lord/*\",\n  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret }),\n);\n\n// Rate limiting — per-wallet and global limits on POST requests\napp.use(\n  \"/coinflip/*\",\n  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n    perWallet: config.rateLimitPerWallet,\n    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n    windowMs: 60_000,\n  }),\n);\napp.use(\n  \"/lord/*\",\n  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n    perWallet: config.rateLimitPerWallet,\n    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n    windowMs: 60_000,\n  }),\n);\n\n// Settlement infrastructure — must be created before routes (routes use pdaWatcher)\nconst entropyAccount = new PublicKey(config.entropyAccount);\nconst retrySettler = createRetrySettler({\n  db,\n  connection,\n  settleRound: (pda) =>\n    settleRound(\n      { db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair, entropyAccount, referralDefaultRateBps: config.referralDefaultRateBps },\n      pda,\n    ),\n});\n\n// PDA watcher — WebSocket-based instant join detection\nconst pdaWatcher = createPdaWatcher({\n  connection,\n  serverKey: config.serverKeypair.publicKey,\n  db,\n  onJoinDetected: async (pda, targetSlot) => {\n    // Update DB phase if still in 'created'\n    const round = await db.getRoundByPda(pda);\n    if (round && round.phase === \"created\") {\n      await db.updateRoundPhase(pda, \"locked\", {\n        target_slot: targetSlot.toString(),\n      });\n      await db.insertOperatorEvent(pda, \"match_detected\", {\n        targetSlot: targetSlot.toString(),\n        source: \"pda-watcher\",\n        game: round.game,\n      });\n    }\n\n    // Check if target slot already passed — settle immediately if so\n    const currentSlot = await connection.getSlot();\n    if (BigInt(currentSlot) >= targetSlot) {\n      await retrySettler.attemptSettle(pda);\n      pdaWatcher.unwatch(pda);\n    }\n    // If target slot not reached yet, poll worker will pick it up next cycle\n  },\n});\n\nconst worker = createSettlementWorker({\n  db,\n  connection,\n  serverKey: config.serverKeypair.publicKey,\n  pollIntervalMs: config.workerPollIntervalMs,\n  onSettleReady: async (pda) => {\n    await retrySettler.attemptSettle(pda);\n    pdaWatcher.unwatch(pda); // clean up subscription after settlement\n  },\n  isFinalized: (pda) => retrySettler.isFinalized(pda),\n});\nworker.start();\n\n// Close Call clock worker — fetches boundary prices + settles open rounds\n// Rounds are created on-demand by players via /closecall/bet\nconst closeCallClock = createCloseCallClockWorker({\n  connection,\n  serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair,\n  db,\n});\ncloseCallClock.start();\n\n// Register event handlers before starting the worker\nregisterHandler(\n  EventTypes.REFERRAL_CLAIM_REQUESTED,\n  createClaimHandler({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair }),\n);\nregisterHandler(\n  EventTypes.GAME_SETTLED,\n  createGameSettledHandler({ db }),\n);\nregisterHandler(\n  EventTypes.REWARD_POOL_FUND,\n  createRewardPoolFundHandler({ db }),\n);\nregisterHandler(\n  EventTypes.POINTS_GRANT,\n  createPointsGrantHandler({\n    db,\n    getSolPrice: async () => {\n      const result = await fetchSolPrice();\n      return result?.price ?? null;\n    },\n  }),\n);\nregisterHandler(\n  EventTypes.CRATE_DROP,\n  createCrateDropHandler({ db }),\n);\n\n// Event queue worker — processes async side-effects (rewards, notifications, etc.)\nconst eventWorker = createEventWorker(sql, {\n  pollIntervalMs: config.eventQueuePollMs,\n});\neventWorker.start();\nlogger.info(\"Event queue worker started\", {\n  pollIntervalMs: config.eventQueuePollMs,\n});\n\n// Game-specific routes\napp.route(\n  \"/coinflip\",\n  createCoinflipRoutes({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair, pdaWatcher }),\n);\napp.route(\n  \"/lord\",\n  createLordRoutes({ db, connection, serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair, pdaWatcher }),\n);\n\n// Close Call — JWT + rate limiting on POST /bet (co-signs with server keypair)\napp.use(\n  \"/closecall/bet\",\n  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret }),\n);\napp.use(\n  \"/closecall/bet\",\n  createRateLimitMiddleware({\n    perWallet: config.rateLimitPerWallet,\n    global: config.rateLimitGlobal,\n    windowMs: 60_000,\n  }),\n);\n\n// Close Call routes (read endpoints are public, /bet is auth'd above)\napp.route(\"/closecall\", createCloseCallRoutes({\n  db,\n  connection,\n  serverKeypair: config.serverKeypair,\n  clockWorker: closeCallClock,\n}));\n\n// Challenge routes — authenticated GET endpoints (require JWT on all methods)\napp.use(\n  \"/challenges/*\",\n  createJwtAuthMiddleware({ jwtSecret: config.jwtSecret, requireAllMethods: true }),\n);\napp.route(\"/challenges\", createChallengeRoutes({ db }));\n\n// Leaderboard routes — public, no auth\napp.route(\"/leaderboard\", createLeaderboardRoutes({ db }));\n\n// Price routes — public, no auth\napp.route(\"/price\", createPriceRoutes());\n\n// Round verification routes\napp.route(\"/rounds\", createRoundsRoutes({ db }));\n\n// Health endpoint — wired after worker exists so we can query its status\napp.route(\n  \"/health\",\n  createHealthRoutes({\n    db,\n    sql,\n    isWorkerRunning: () => worker.isRunning,\n  }),\n);\n\n// Internal admin routes — only registered when ADMIN_TOKEN is set (dev/devnet only)\nif (config.adminToken) {\n  app.route(\"/internal\", createInternalRoutes({ config, sql }));\n  logger.warn(\"Admin routes enabled at /internal — do NOT set ADMIN_TOKEN in production\");\n}\n\nconst port = config.port;\nlogger.info(\"fairness-backend started\", { port });\n\nserve({\n  fetch: app.fetch,\n  port,\n  hostname: \"0.0.0.0\",\n});\n\nexport default {\n  port,\n  fetch: app.fetch,\n};\n","numLines":325,"startLine":1,"totalLines":325}}}
