{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019h13rcyvf7wgj4ZrUjBinN","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t/**\n2\t * Hono environment type augmentation for custom context variables.\n3\t *\n4\t * userId: set by JWT middleware (from token sub claim).\n5\t * Wallet is NOT in context — routes that need wallet resolve it from the player profile.\n6\t */\n7\t\n8\texport type AppEnv = {\n9\t  Variables: {\n10\t    userId: string;\n11\t  };\n12\t};\n13\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2e700c10-4389-4a9a-beb2-50db732591da","uuid":"b60e8edf-7af4-46bb-b9c0-ecf2fb748e1b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:52:47.602Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/hono-env.ts","content":"/**\n * Hono environment type augmentation for custom context variables.\n *\n * userId: set by JWT middleware (from token sub claim).\n * Wallet is NOT in context — routes that need wallet resolve it from the player profile.\n */\n\nexport type AppEnv = {\n  Variables: {\n    userId: string;\n  };\n};\n","numLines":13,"startLine":1,"totalLines":13}}}
