{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01R3rzpK2xwRsBBEvP8Np6jC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Mx7yLmmTDX5oiaV19pkBBj","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/400-challenge-engine/spec.md","old_string":"- [ ] [backend] Implement `GET /points/mine` (JWT auth, returns `{balance, lifetimeEarned}` from player_points — return zeros if no row), `GET /points/mine/history` (JWT auth, paginated point_grants rows DESC by created_at with source_type, source_id, amount, metadata, created_at), `GET /crates/mine` (JWT auth, paginated crate_drops rows DESC by created_at with crate_type, contents_amount, status, created_at, granted_at). Use standard pagination pattern (cursor or offset+limit). Integration test: seed test data, verify response shapes; verify pagination; verify empty state returns correctly. Verify: `cd backend && pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck && pnpm test` (FR-14)","new_string":"- [x] [backend] Implement `GET /points/mine` (JWT auth, returns `{balance, lifetimeEarned}` from player_points — return zeros if no row), `GET /points/mine/history` (JWT auth, paginated point_grants rows DESC by created_at with source_type, source_id, amount, metadata, created_at), `GET /crates/mine` (JWT auth, paginated crate_drops rows DESC by created_at with crate_type, contents_amount, status, created_at, granted_at). Use standard pagination pattern (cursor or offset+limit). Integration test: seed test data, verify response shapes; verify pagination; verify empty state returns correctly. Verify: `cd backend && pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck && pnpm test` (FR-14) (done: iteration 12)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":457,"cache_read_input_tokens":77586,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":457},"output_tokens":1,"servic